  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“The common people pray for rain, healthy children, and a summer that never ends. It is no matter to them if the high lords play their <b>game of thrones</b>, so long as they are left in peace. They never are.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23233.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23233.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot23233.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot23233.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 23\">Chapter 23</a>, Daenerys III, 233.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404034112\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 71/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8424/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 326/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 34/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 469/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.667      1 -total\n100.00%    4.667      1 Template:Ref\n 65.55%    3.059      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:13679-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404034112 and revision id 275292\n -->\n",
